                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Statistics Tile -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6"
                 style="background-image:url(../images/statistics.jpg); background-size:100%; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
                <h3 style="color: black;">Statistics</h3><br />
                <p>
                    Do you want to learn statistics for data science without taking a slow and expensive
                    course?<br /><br />
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark"
                       href="https://elitedatascience.com/learn-statistics-for-data-science">
                        Read more
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Machine Learning Tile -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6"
                 style="background-image:url(../images/machine_learning.jpg); background-size:100%; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
                <h3>Machine Learning</h3><br />
                <p>
                    Machine Learning is a growing field that is used when searching the web, placing ads, credit
                    scoring, stock trading and for many other applications.<br /><br />
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark"
                       href="https://www.edx.org/course/machine-learning-data-science-analytics-1">
                        Read more
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Programming Languages Visualisation Tile -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6"
                 style="background-image:url(../images/programming_languages.jpg); background-size:100%; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
                <h3>Programming Languages</h3>
                <p>
                    With a high demand for Data Scientists in industries, there is a need for people who possess the
                    required skills in order to become proficient in this field.<br /><br />
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark"
                       href="https://medium.com/datadriveninvestor/top-6-data-science-programming-languages-for-2019-39ba1b6819a8">
                        Read more
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Data Analysis Tile -->
